### Micro Marketplace API Tests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
@productId = YOUR_PRODUCT_ID_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New User",
  "email": "newuser@test.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

###

### Login User 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@test.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

###

### Login User 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user2@test.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

###

### Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get All Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

###

### Get Products with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?search=headphones

###

### Get Products with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&limit=5

###

### Get Products by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?category=Electronics

###

### Get Products - Combined Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?search=watch&category=Electronics&page=1&limit=10

###

### Get Single Product
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/{{productId}}

###

### Get User Favorites
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/favorites
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Add Product to Favorites
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/favorites/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Remove Product from Favorites
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/favorites/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create New Product (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Product",
